caption.text:
How blessed i am, to have someone that makes goodbye is such a very hard word to say. 
Just thank you for everything, for the ups and downs in our 14-years-friendship we've been through together, for being the most amazing and best girl friend of mine (anyone couldn't ever imagine). I won't write all my messages for you here, because it'll gonna be a super loooong one. Nevertheless, one thing for sure is my prayer will always be with you. May every aspects of your life always be showered by God's grace. And we'll always have each other's back no matter how far the distance might separate us, right?

Sad to realize that someone who has a big place in my heart is separated from me for miles. But there's nothing makes me happier than seeing you standing in the closer step from your own dreams.

Best of luck and be the best student u can be in HK, bestie! Don't ever give up when life is hard. And you'll be always in the top list of people who i miss too muchüòäüòò see you when i see you, God bless!
